{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"652","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"《證交所》2月上市公司營收年減4.12％，半導體、生技、食品逆風飛","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>08:02&nbsp; 2020/03/11&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>時報資訊 莊丙農</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>台灣證券交易所初步統計，受疫情影響，上市公司<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月營收總計<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>8,800</span>億元，年減<span lang='EN-US'>4.12</span>％，不過，主力產業的半導體單月營收年增<span lang='EN-US'>34.59</span>％，而防疫股的生技股營收也有年增<span lang='EN-US'>8.01</span>％表現。證交所表示，上市公司大陸營運據點大部分均已復工，產能逐漸恢復，將可提振業績。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>台灣上市公司共有<span lang='EN-US'>866</span>家、第一上市公司有<span lang='EN-US'>76</span>家，證交所昨日傍晚統計<span lang='EN-US'>832</span>家國內上市公司及<span lang='EN-US'>67</span>家第一上市公司，<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月營收總計<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>8,800</span>億元，年減<span lang='EN-US'>808</span>億元，年減幅<span lang='EN-US'>4.12</span>％，營收成長公司共<span lang='EN-US'>451</span>家，衰退公司共<span lang='EN-US'>448</span>家；這<span lang='EN-US'>899</span>家公司前<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月累計營收總計<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>3,135</span>億元，年減<span lang='EN-US'>3,949</span>億元，年減幅<span lang='EN-US'>8.39</span>％，營收成長公司共<span lang='EN-US'>294</span>家，衰退公司共<span lang='EN-US'>605</span>家。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>證交所指出，上市公司營收雖受疫情衝擊，惟個別產業表現各有不同，其中個別公司營收變化仍視其接單與生產基地分布狀況而定。而我國主力產業半導體單月及累計前<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月營收分別年成長<span lang='EN-US'>34.59</span>％及<span lang='EN-US'>24.32</span>％，主要個別公司客戶需求增加。另外，防疫類股相關的生技醫療業<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月營收較年成長<span lang='EN-US'>8.01</span>％，內需相關食品工業<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月營收亦年成長<span lang='EN-US'>5.78</span>％。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>證交所也統計，受新冠疫情影響復工情形方面，上市公司大陸營運據點大部分均已復工，目前產能逐漸恢復中，且上市公司營收已連兩年創下佳績，去年全體上市公司營收總計<span lang='EN-US'>32</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>7,667</span>億元，連兩年超過<span lang='EN-US'>32</span>兆大關，未來如果疫情趨緩，各產業應能儘速恢復產能。<span lang='EN-US'>(</span>時報資訊<span lang='EN-US'>)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200311001315-260410?chdtv</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-03-11","clk_count":"174"}},"__N_SSG":true}